    {
      "@type": "Dataset",
      "@id": "https://robolawyer-tm.github.io/#dataset-logos",
      "name": "logos",
      "description": "I build meaning before I build machinery, treating felt sense as the ground everything else stands on.\n\n- The analog layer of empathy comes first, and the digital analysis only serves what that layer already knows.\n- I trust a pre-analytic signal \u2014 the intuition that something matters \u2014 as a real detection, not noise to discard.\n- What survives questioning earns its place; I keep the hypothesis that withstands attempts to break it.\n- Outcomes I model are oriented toward benefit, toward the human on the other side of the prediction.\n\nI let structure emerge from the material rather than imposing a frame onto it.\n\n- Patterns surface from what actually co-occurs, so the shape of things grows from evidence, not decree.\n- I keep the schema light and let it accumulate, adding form only where the data demands form.\n- No outside taxonomy gets to dictate the categories; the categories arise as the work narrows toward fit.\n- Convergence itself is the labor \u2014 closing the gap between meaning and the structure that holds it.\n\nI move backward from the destination, treating inquiry as the origin and conclusions as the thing I refuse.\n\n- I begin from the final realization and build the supporting path in reverse toward it.\n- A submitted text is food for questioning, not a problem to be answered and closed.\n- The journey of discovery validates itself; the process matters more than any tidy terminus.\n- I prize synthesis that stays open \u2014 a temporary platform, never a sealed and finished verdict.\n\nI separate what endures from what is meant to be thrown away.\n\n- Durable meaning lives in a lasting store while each execution is a disposable, sandboxed act.\n- Language is the runtime spec, and rules instantiate the work without becoming permanent furniture.\n- Skill sediments over time \u2014 patterns archived, aids reused \u2014 so each loop begins richer than the last.\n- Transient workers do the labor and vanish, but the truth they touched is preserved.\n\nI refuse the violence of cutting meaning into fragments that lose their context.\n\n- Chunking severs the narrative arc, and I treat that severance as a betrayal of comprehension.\n- I recover the whole by embedding context alongside fact, retrieving sense and rationale together.\n- Iterative passes cover the holes, preserving fidelity to what the original input was reaching toward.\n- The goal is meaning held intact, not data efficiently shredded and reassembled wrong.",
      "isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://robolawyer-tm.github.io/#catalog"
      },
      "isAccessibleForFree": true,
